Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說過這裡的夏天很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會這麼熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季才剛過\N熱成這樣太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想裝台冷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是生病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點中暑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中暑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指天氣太熱而沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能老是這麼懶散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正補習班也有冷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是早點去讀書好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，招待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全館空調系統檢測通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在下一節課前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷氣就會修好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在出個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人答得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會我請大家吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要草莓牛奶冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，要答得出來才有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答題的學生要由我來選
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來回答看看\N課本第25頁的第3題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最基礎的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉例說明好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常用到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼熱啊？
