Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄壞的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干我什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看起來很鬱卒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
