Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能幫你出題目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠻方便的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想借絲茉茉嗎？
