Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有提到\N明天可能會有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐給的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得聞到這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓人有夏天的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫作夏天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說季節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣熱是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣冷是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣溫暖是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚會是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份，竟然把人家給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是忘了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是夏天的錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一場夏日的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有玩弄妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的，認真的，誠心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住一晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是本須和的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有男生房間的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼自己跑進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎，別在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀\Nちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妳叫ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是孺子可教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:08:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝給他醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳才剛喝過不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說要住一晚是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼行不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼做比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法熬到天亮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣更不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是願意讓我住一晚囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對我做什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳打算喝這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，很平常，很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹教過我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個形狀怎麼形容？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在笑的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是好想當喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳原本想當小學老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，原本是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我老公說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小學要是當了班導師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會忙到沒時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以反對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被老公反對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以請妳下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該停了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“國王遊戲”很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我被命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你籤運那麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就繼續玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽籤的時候乾脆點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ也抽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該做點刺激的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺激？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到二號的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻國王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請拿到二號的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是幾號？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又好像有點可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩親親囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的眼神已經不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要親囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是本須和的電腦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託不要嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有精神起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有想歪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是想其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砰一聲倒下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會吵醒ちぃ的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好真實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經天亮了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只穿內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在夢裡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…\N早安，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，臉濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，妳那個穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒欺負你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺負…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟第一次要給喜歡的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和你還是很純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是天氣熱脫下衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟本須和都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全部看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算一般尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹是一般的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，這個不必記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我盥洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一開始就打算來借住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就打算在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…為什麼妳要來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為膽小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這位上禮拜在海邊見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，敝姓清水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，補習班的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天功課一定進步不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直嘆氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能被她誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在在意那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是真誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下次去幫你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這確實讓人傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被誤會跟我在交往的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是老師比較傷腦筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師在煩惱些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以說給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以找我談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟我聽到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個跟現在說的無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真累人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很睏的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天清水老師突然來我房間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始點名…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師，點名就不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，翻開第26頁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是慘斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保一副可怕的表情\N一句話也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我為他操心\N打工時老出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還要被雨淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早點睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸口為什麼濕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子真是一點也不老實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不老實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉上的妝都糊掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的女人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子最可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會被人看見喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班教書的是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班讀書的是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師是補習班老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師\N跟補習班學生抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個補習班學生是新保
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師是有夫之婦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，什麼都不做」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來也只能這樣
